@DATABASE CLOCKLIB
@Author Conversion program
@NODE OVERVIEW "Overview of CLOCKLIB"

                                  @{b}@{u}Overview@{ub}@{uu}


                      A Vernoux Benjamin Software Library

          Edited, fixed and cleaned by Benjamin Vernoux 15/04/2000.
          
